        <div class="news-des">
           <p><span node-type="summary">　　就算是手机，单纯跑分也不能反应性能好坏，何况是人呢？</span><a class="CC-theme" target="_blank" href="http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/laliga/2019-09-20/doc-iicezueu7082834.shtml">[详情]</a></p>
