      <dt class="news-tit ellipsis" data-level=" item-important"><a target="_blank" href="http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/pl/2019-09-03/doc-iicezzrq3157433.shtml">还说瓜帅只靠烧钱？皇马巴萨穆帅渣叔都会怼你的</a></dt>
	  
            <dd class="news-con col1">
        <a class="news-img" target="_blank" href="http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/pl/2019-09-03/doc-iicezzrq3157433.shtml">
          <img alt="还说瓜帅只靠烧钱？皇马巴萨穆帅渣叔都会怼你的" src="http://k.sinaimg.cn/n/sports/transform/215/w650h365/20190903/14a3-ieaiqii4646430.jpg/w180h135l50t17ac.jpg">
        </a>
        <div class="news-des">
           <p><span node-type="summary">　　现在这个疯狂烧钱的时代，能把高价引援带好，又能激活新亮点，你以为那么容易？</span><a class="CC-theme" target="_blank" href="http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/pl/2019-09-03/doc-iicezzrq3157433.shtml">[详情]</a></p>
