  <dt><a target="_blank" href="http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/laliga/2019-09-20/doc-iicezueu7082834.shtml">别让机器评分骗了！只看这个黑武磊还是歇歇吧</a></dt>
  <dd>
    <a target="_blank" href="http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/laliga/2019-09-20/doc-iicezueu7082834.shtml">
